^ Dalgarno, S. J.; Tucker, SA; Bassil, DB; Atwood, JL. Fluorescent Guest Molecules Report Ordered Inner Phase of Host Capsules in Solution. Science. 2005, 309 (5743): 2037. PMID 16179474. doi:10.1126/science.1116579. 
