^ Meyers, M.A., Chen. Biological Materials: Structure and Mechanical Properties. Prog. Mat. Sci. 2008, 53: 1–206. doi:10.1016/j.pmatsci.2007.05.002. 
^ Heuer, A.H.; 等. Innovative Materials Processing Strategies: A Biomimetic Approach. Science. 1992, 255: 1098. doi:10.1126/science.1546311.  引文格式1維護：顯式使用等標簽 (link)


